It is a basic questiion from the topic string but it has been asked in the interview 

Given a string S. For each index i(1<=i<=N-1), erase it if s[i] is equal to s[i-1] in the string.


    string removeConsecutiveCharacter(string S)
    {
        // code here.
        string str ;
        for(int i = 0; i<S.size(); i++){
            
            if(S[i] == S[i+1]){
                continue;
            }
            else{
                str.push_back(S[i]);
            }
        }
        return str;
    }
